				{
					"type": "thinking_start"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "The",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " user is asking me to write a 300 word essay on agentic AI context management. This is a creative/informational writing task, not a coding task. Let",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " me think about this topic and write an essay.\n\nAgentic AI context management refers to how autonomous AI",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " agents maintain, update, and utilize context during extended interactions or tasks. This is an important topic in AI systems",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " design.\n\nLet me write this essay now.",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_stop"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "# Agentic AI Context Management\n\nAgentic AI systems—aut",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "onomous agents capable of reasoning, planning, and executing multi-step tasks—face a fundamental challenge: maintaining",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " coherent context across extended operations. Unlike simple request-response interactions, agentic workflows require persistent,",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " evolving awareness of goals, intermediate states, and environmental feedback.\n\n## The Core Challenge\n\n",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "Context management for agentic systems spans multiple dimensions. **Working memory** must track the current",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " task state—what's been attempted, what's succeeded, what remains. **Semantic context",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "** preserves the meaning and intent behind user requests, preventing the system from losing sight of the broader objective",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " amid granular subtasks. **Episodic memory** enables the agent to recall prior interactions within",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " a session, building toward cumulative understanding rather than treating each exchange as isolated.\n\nTraditional approaches",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " relied on fixed context windows, but this creates artificial boundaries. An agent working",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " on a complex codebase can't meaningfully contribute if it can only see the most recent messages. The solution lies",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " in architectural patterns that treat context as a first-class concern: hierarchical memory systems, selective",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " retrieval mechanisms, and explicit state management.\n\n## Architectural Approaches\n\nEffective context management typically employs a",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " layered strategy. The **immediate layer** handles the active conversation window—what's",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " currently in focus. A **retrieval layer** pulls relevant historical information on demand, using embeddings",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " or structured queries to surface pertinent past context. A **summarization layer** compresses older information into distilled",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " forms, preserving essential patterns without overwhelming the working context.\n\nSome systems implement **",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "checkpointing**—periodically saving structured representations of agent state that can be restored or consulted later. Others use",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " **tool-augmented memory**, where the agent itself decides what to remember by writing to external stores",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ".\n\n## The Attention Problem\n\nPerhaps the most sophisticated aspect of agentic context management is determining *",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "what matters*. An agent processing a codebase across hundreds of files can't treat",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " all information equally. Attention mechanisms—whether learned or heuristic—help the",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " agent focus on contextually relevant signals while filtering noise.\n\nThe future",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " of agentic AI context management lies in systems that are **proactively self-aware**",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "—continuously evaluating what context to maintain, what to discard, and what to synthesize. The goal",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " isn't more context, but *better* context: precise, actionable, and aligned with the",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " task at hand.",
					"messageId": "msg_d291a0e7b001wN0a7JTMDtdVV5"
				},
